description:
In 048ed2d deployed on http://ruian.linked.opendata.cz/sparql when I run this query:

select ?amnumber ?nazevulice ?cisloD ?cisloO ?psc ?nazevobce ?nazevvusc where
{
?am a ruian:AdresniMisto ;
    skos:notation ?amnumber ;
    ruian:psc ?psc .
OPTIONAL { ?am ruian:cisloDomovni ?cisloD . }
OPTIONAL { ?am ruian:cisloOrientacni ?cisloO . }
OPTIONAL {?am ruian:ulice ?ulice .
  ?ulice a ruian:Ulice ;
    s:name ?nazevulice .
OPTIONAL { ?ulice ruian:obec ?obec .
  ?obec a ruian:Obec ;
    s:name ?nazevobce .
OPTIONAL { ?obec ruian:pou/ruian:orp/ruian:vusc ?vusc .
  ?vusc a ruian:Vusc ;
    s:name ?nazevvusc .}
}
}
}

I get 1 048 578 results (e.g. as a CSV file).
However, when I count the results like this (only the first row changed):

select count (distinct ?amnumber) where
{
?am a ruian:AdresniMisto ;
    skos:notation ?amnumber ;
    ruian:psc ?psc .
OPTIONAL { ?am ruian:cisloDomovni ?cisloD . }
OPTIONAL { ?am ruian:cisloOrientacni ?cisloO . }
OPTIONAL {?am ruian:ulice ?ulice .
  ?ulice a ruian:Ulice ;
    s:name ?nazevulice .
OPTIONAL { ?ulice ruian:obec ?obec .
  ?obec a ruian:Obec ;
    s:name ?nazevobce .
OPTIONAL { ?obec ruian:pou/ruian:orp/ruian:vusc ?vusc .
  ?vusc a ruian:Vusc ;
    s:name ?nazevvusc .}
}
}
}

the answer is 2 894 126.
I thought this was an issue with ResultSetMaxRows virtuoso.ini, but that is set to 10000000000.
The database is the same one as in #200 only with 2 added prefixes:
s: http://schema.org/
ruian: http://ruian.linked.opendata.cz/ontology/
